VERIFICATION
State of New York
County of Rockland
SS:
Anthony Castello, being duly sworn, deposes and says that deponent is the
President of Casco Contracting Corp herein, that deponent has read the foregoing
notice of lien and knows the contents thereof, and that the same is true to deponent's
own knowledge, except as to the matters therein stated to be alleged upon information
and belief and that as to those matters, deponent believes it to be true.
The reason why this verification is made by deponent is that deponent is an
officer, to wit, the President of Casco Contracting Corp. which is a domestic
corporation and is familiar with the facts and circumstances herein.
And the sources of deponent's information and grounds of deponent's belief as
to all matters not therein stated upon deponent's knowledge are as follows: a copy of
the complete file within the corporation relating to the project and communications
with the owner.
Sworn to before me this
48_day of February 2022.
Tommarce Nestive
Notary Public - State of New York
ANTHONY CASTELLO
TONIMARIE NASTRI
NOTARY PUBLIC STATE OF NEW YORK
No 01NA6330280
Qualified in Rockland County
My Commission Expires September 14, 2028
